title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 24
description:
This video explores the newest updates in the MSFS marketplace. This week, the marketplace has expanded with several new aircraft, including a helicopter. Additionally, there are new livery packs for the A320 V2 and a cockpit upgrade. The marketplace also offers mission packs, training packs, and the latest airport updates.
